Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Several months after that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We live on the land named Amazon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In this mysterious place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as if he lost himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried his best to look for gold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on, all is our time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and we spend our time with Huamu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room for me in his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He always looks to the faraway place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as if his heart was covered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,by a dark curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He called himself avenger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}I'll{\i0} follow him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,even I lose my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kouxiaxihu,\Ncan give up my auditorship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as a reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Ice Race
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,living nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the battle between them\Nand the invading Northern Step Race
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ice Race
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, ifs a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the real ID of Huamu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}901{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous Stars of American Soccer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was arrested because of hiding drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(The molder of a super star )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Commit Suicide With lover)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one of them died, is it a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The emeer of Ice Race
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to show thanks to him\Nfor driving away the other race
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he said that he'd share us some treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hide“ by him{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortune of Kingdom Portugal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which colonized Brazil before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have heart about the legend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,about that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your survival purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The super star
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,abandoned by the world a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Cimuguijie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So your name is Cimuguijie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} tell you why I call myself Avenger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just because of\Nthe woman who hurted me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was an international student\Nin USA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a vanguard in a soccer team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always ranked first
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter in USA or Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided\NI must join American Professional Team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just\Nin the last summer of my collegehood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become the best team of USA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we took part in a match in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I met Xiazi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Cimuguijie of the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you fall in love with Xiazi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,\NI don't care what famous star you are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a soccer player
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can you have a match with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can stop the trolley\Nwith your shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think ifs OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Miss Xiazi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,really falls into love with him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this kind of man\Nsuits to her very much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the beginning of\Nthe short summer of Xiazi and me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?\NWhy do you run here suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The football thrown out by you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,caused a scar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that it won't disappear forever
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel sorry,\Nplease tattoo me in it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to tattoo me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This... Oops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I like blue lizard most
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gentle to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my first lover
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!\NWhat do you want to do? Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, we were attacked by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and taken to a villa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We began to doubt our eyes suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a super star of world fame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And there're many men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The professional athleted,\Nthe champion of Olympic Game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The worlds famous movie star
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The professional athleted,\Nthe champion of Olympic Game
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a famous star
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ifs the premonition of one episode\Njust now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And there're many others too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,GPX
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(Super Blue Movie)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Performed by famous actors
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best blue movie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who're you'?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us these movies.\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're attracting you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to act as Cimuguijie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the famous soccer player
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and USA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're selected as the glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,star of the next movie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And she
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is your competitor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course ifs not free
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the performance fee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse! No way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do like that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose your popularity\Nin the future
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of your threat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the next few days
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was set by the heels\Nand I didn't have any food
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What' re you doing'?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Don't hurt her any more
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you promised to play the role?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie, you can't lose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You must act in that movie.\NI won't let you pass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie, get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll burn you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm burnt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't perform in that movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't damage\Nthe important merchandise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but to\Nsleep with a woman for one time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can get Cimuguijie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiazi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie, you brought much herion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and marijuana to sell in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with your auditorship as\Nan international student
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We found 1 kg herion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when we searched your home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd applied for\Nthe wanted oder earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd not kill your wife\Nonly because of profit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How come... ifs so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie who broke the drugs rules
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed one person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a crime,\Nand will be prisoned for 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some evidence I never saw
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I learnt in prison that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cimuguijie! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After serving my sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I left Japan for Brazil
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get the gold for the avenge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked if I could make\Na 70-foot ship myself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who're you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bluster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best ship manufacture expert
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in Bilian
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can settle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,any problem myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you were introduced by Luobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the partners of those\Nwho smuggled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to go to USA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum, do you want to stow away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe Luobi too much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the subscription
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who're you'?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The hair is all white
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... It seems good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, we invited\Nthis woman architectural expert
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we make a ship in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these to USA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't let anyone ese know it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'd guise the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with the gold and treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reward is one third of\Nthe treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too little
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} piss as long as I see gold
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've devorced three times for it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you promise? Biji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} make a gold ship for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know although gold is very heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ifs very weak for swash and grind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And its heat-resistance ability\Nis also very excellent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we melt it\Nand use is as the balancer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be found
